'''Welspun USA Inc''' is a subsidiary of India based [[Welspun India Ltd]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thisweeknews.com/live/content/grovecity/stories/2009/06/24/0625grwelspun_ln.html |title=Agreement keeps Welspun in Grove City &#124; ThisWeek Community Newspapers |publisher=|date=2009-06-24 |accessdate=2011-01-06}}</ref> One of the largest marketers of the USD 3 billion [[Welspun Group]]'s home textile products globally. Its products includes for Bath Towels, Bath, Accent & Scatter rugs, Down & Synthetic filled Comforters/Blankets, and Pillows & Mattress pads.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/nexcen-brands-inc-announces-strategic-partnership-with-welspun-usa-to-expand-waverly-brand-57128397.html |title=NexCen Brands, Inc., Announces Strategic Partnership with Welspun USA to Expand Waverly... - re> NEW YORK, Jan. 22 /PRNewswire-FirstCall/ |location=New York |publisher=Prnewswire.com |date=2008-01-21 |accessdate=2011-01-06}}</ref> It was established in 2000, as a wholly owned subsidiary of [[Welspun Retail Ltd]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/welspun-india-ltd/infocompanyhistory/companyid-12096.cms |title=WELSPUNIND History &#124; Welspun India Ltd Company History & Profile |publisher=Economictimes.indiatimes.com |date= |accessdate=2011-02-18}}</ref>
